useradd/adduser name
groupadd/addgroup name
id username
cat/etc/passwd - list of users(getent passwd)
cat/etc/groups - list of groups (getent group)
deluser/userdel name
delgroup/groupdel name
passwd username
usermod -aG groupname username(add user in agroup)
su - username(switch user)
CHANGE OWNERS:
chown username filename
chgrp groupname filename
chown username:groupname filename(change user&group at atime)
